      "id": "d615faf4-28ea-43a5-91d2-1e93a7667010",
      "title": "Create unified test artifacts folder and document target HDF5 schema",
      "description": "Create con vert/test_artifacts/ folder. Document the 16 streams (4 frame rates: 60/50/20/10 Hz), 10 vector + 3 image + 3 gripper groups, per-stream timestamps format, and verify all 179 JPEGs have valid SOI/EOI markers. Write schema.json capturing all metadata needed by downstream converters.",
