      "notes": "The target HDF5 has ASYNCHRONOUS streams: VR@60Hz(1119), IK@50Hz(820), arm@20Hz(358), camera@10Hz(179). Timestamps are uint64 nanosecond epoch, NOT frame-aligned. Each stream has independent timestamps. This is critical for converter design.",
